body:
### PSU MacAdmins 2014 - Shell Building Blocks
This repo contains supporting material for my "Shell Building Blocks" talk. You'll find extended talk notes, example scripts, and links to some of my favorite online resources for learning the shell.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
